3. ZMIANY W KODZIE

3.1. NOWA funkcja centralna (KLUCZOWA)

Dodaj np. do utils_clients.py (albo runnera na start):

def resolve_clients(all_clients, include=None, exclude=None):
    """
    all_clients: iterable (np. z DB)
    include: list | None
    exclude: list | None
    """
    all_clients = set(all_clients)
    if include:
        clients = set(include)
    else:
        clients = all_clients
    if exclude:
        clients = clients - set(exclude)
    return sorted(list(clients))

