3.7. FIRST MODEL — SQL FILTER

Rozszerz:

def build_client_filter_sql(params):
    col = params.get('test_client_id_column')
    ids = params.get('test_client_id')
    if col and ids:
        ids_sql = ",".join(str(i) for i in ids)
        return f" AND {col} IN ({ids_sql})"
    return ""

